{"tid":525674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美駐古巴外交人員或遭病毒攻擊","createTime":"2018-01-11T02:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-11T09:29:05.000Z","uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0696ebf0102de552bb8105a7609395fda6a59ee1","tid":525674,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T02:10:15.000Z","msg":"美駐古巴外交人員或遭病毒攻擊<br />\n<br />\n美國駐古巴外交人員集體聽力受損奇案發生逾一年，華府前日否定肇因是聲波攻擊的說法，但堅稱有攻擊，指也有可能由病毒引致。<br />\n<br />\n找不到聲波攻擊證據<br />\n24名美國駐夏灣拿外交人員及其家屬，前年秋季起相繼出現聽力受損、暈眩、頭痛、失眠等症狀。國務院官員前日到國會參議院外交關係委員會作供，外交安全助理總監布朗（Todd Brown）指，大多數受影響人員都報稱聽過怪聲，但聲音不是病因。美聯社周一取得的聯邦調查局（FBI）調查報告亦指，美方找不到聲波危害人員健康的證據，但有調查人員指聲音或由發動攻擊的裝置發出。<br />\n<br />\n布朗又謂目前仍有許多可能性未被排除，包括有人刻意讓美方外交人員感染病毒，但他沒提供相關證據。他又強調，創傷很可能由攻擊造成，難以相信古巴政府不知事件原因和始作俑者。國務院首席醫生羅森法爾布（Charles Rosenfarb）就肯定事件不是集體錯覺。<br />\n<br />\n古巴外交部美國事務主管維達爾（Josefina Vidal）否認夏灣拿政府涉事或知情，更指連月調查顯示攻擊根本不存在，聆訊破壞真相<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180111/20270770\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180111%2F20270770&d=rAtfao6yB4dxNkpNzqY3kAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=ecf5eb54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180111%2F20270770&h=c3c860b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180111/20270770</a>"},{"pid":"1cfba78b30b488fd0334d93a7668e89eb4fb4d2b","tid":525674,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T02:13:05.000Z","msg":"傳說中嘅蠱毒"},{"pid":"8e9deb63826026455861081bc9e6e1eceae90d24","tid":525674,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T02:13:16.000Z","msg":"會唔會係重金屬中毒，啲症狀似係"},{"pid":"e2a253ea5d3302ce9fbb358a9a00449aa6ebeb68","tid":525674,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T02:21:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會係重金屬中毒，啲症狀似係</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n金屬中毒應該好易驗到<br />\n可能有其他新野"},{"pid":"671f85445e21122acee4ea03c0b92b71264bd4ae","tid":525674,"uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T02:44:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumb9.shutterstock.com/display_pic_with_logo/351577/680173066/stock-photo-moscow-russia-july-rare-stamp-printed-in-cuba-shows-cinchona-flower-plant-and-crystal-680173066.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumb9.shutterstock.com%2Fdisplay_pic_with_logo%2F351577%2F680173066%2Fstock-photo-moscow-russia-july-rare-stamp-printed-in-cuba-shows-cinchona-flower-plant-and-crystal-680173066.jpg&h=6fafada2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n古巴巫師常用嘅金雞納樹<br />\n<br />\n而Quinidine 係金雞納樹皮提煉出嚟治療瘧疾藥物，有耳毒性<br />\n<br />\n中毒症狀包括耳鳴、頭暈、視力障礙、聽力障礙、複視及噁心等"},{"pid":"3427d8c82d0974bcf97fa2d00ba9ed6c18c37a5a","tid":525674,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T02:57:22.000Z","msg":"起先被形容成是由某種聲波裝置所發出的這項攻擊，過去數月已影響至少22名美國駐哈瓦那大使館館員。<br />\n<br />\n他們出現的生理症狀包括聽力受損、頭暈目眩、耳鳴、平衡問題、視力毛病、頭痛、疲倦、認知問題及難以入眠等。"},{"pid":"668e60966ae72cbb0ede6cb02fb03142d23995f3","tid":525674,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"671f85445e21122acee4ea03c0b92b71264bd4ae","tid":525674,"uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T02:44:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumb9.shutterstock.com/display_pic_with_logo/351577/680173066/stock-photo-moscow-russia-july-rare-stamp-printed-in-cuba-shows-cinchona-flower-plant-and-crystal-680173066.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumb9.shutterstock.com%2Fdisplay_pic_with_logo%2F351577%2F680173066%2Fstock-photo-moscow-russia-july-rare-stamp-printed-in-cuba-shows-cinchona-flower-plant-and-crystal-680173066.jpg&h=6fafada2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n古巴巫師常用嘅金雞納樹<br />\n<br />\n而Quinidine 係金雞納樹皮提煉出嚟治療瘧疾藥物，有耳毒性<br />\n<br />\n中毒症狀包括耳鳴、頭暈、視力障礙、聽力障礙、複視及噁心等"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T02:59:04.000Z","msg":"case closed"},{"pid":"3b13e5ea72271208cfa8f907185f4bb5765de640","tid":525674,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"668e60966ae72cbb0ede6cb02fb03142d23995f3","tid":525674,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"671f85445e21122acee4ea03c0b92b71264bd4ae","tid":525674,"uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T02:44:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumb9.shutterstock.com/display_pic_with_logo/351577/680173066/stock-photo-moscow-russia-july-rare-stamp-printed-in-cuba-shows-cinchona-flower-plant-and-crystal-680173066.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumb9.shutterstock.com%2Fdisplay_pic_with_logo%2F351577%2F680173066%2Fstock-photo-moscow-russia-july-rare-stamp-printed-in-cuba-shows-cinchona-flower-plant-and-crystal-680173066.jpg&h=6fafada2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n古巴巫師常用嘅金雞納樹<br />\n<br />\n而Quinidine 係金雞納樹皮提煉出嚟治療瘧疾藥物，有耳毒性<br />\n<br />\n中毒症狀包括耳鳴、頭暈、視力障礙、聽力障礙、複視及噁心等"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T02:59:04.000Z","msg":"case closed"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T09:29:05.000Z","msg":"純粹猜測<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n班美國佬個個大腦white matter有異常  可能感染或者中毒造成<br />\n<br />\n唔似聲波攻擊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論如何，美國佬都係抵死，派間諜去古巴刺探情報，畀古巴佬玩死"}]}